GPLVote::SignDoc::Client version 0.5
===============

GPLVote::SignDoc::Client - module for create GPLVote SignDoc
clients. This module implement cryptographic and ather functions
for easy create client software.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Crypt::OpenSSL::RSA;
  Crypt::OpenSSL::AES;
  Crypt::CBC;
  Bytes::Random::Secure;
  MIME::Base64;
  LWP::UserAgent;
  JSON;
  Digest::SHA;

